metadata.description: This NFT will give you access to Full Node, a co-working space for blockchain and web 3.0 initiatives, founded by Tendermint and Gnosis. Once you click redeem under “My Things”, this is when your time starts so please only press when you are at the reception on your first day. We look forward to seeing this process unfold. Welcome to the future! Thanks, Gnosis for sponsoring this. More info: https://www.fullnode.berlin/
metadata.name: Full Node Berlin Month Pass
